WorkItem.Description:
This is probably a big PITA to solve, but the Throne of the Four Winds "random" enchant items are not in the cache, and require manual adding/editing after each upgrade. After that, they work correctly.
 
Item example: #63503
 
(This is probably a minor issue, since it is situational, and the items are far from BiS. However, I don't doubt Blizzard will give us more pieces like this on later tiers)
WorkItem.Summary: [Items] Throne of the Four Winds items not getting saved correctly (item cache)
